Get a situation report on the tidymass

tidymass_sitrep.Rd

This function gives a quick overview of the versions of R and RStudio as well as all tidymass packages. It's primarily designed to help you get a quick idea of what's going on when you're helping someone else debug a problem.

Usage

tidymass_sitrep()
